V0424_01_00_00_0.text:
I'm Mizar!
The last Duelist you will ever face!

V0424_01_00_01_0.text: Accept this Duel so I can prove I'm superior to you!

V0424_01_00_02_0.text: You must be insane to think you can defeat Neo Tachyon.

V0424_01_00_03_0.text: No monster is mightier than Neo Galaxy-Eyes Tachyon Dragon!

V0424_01_00_04_0.text:
My Duel Disk's ready!
Prepare for the battle of your life!

V0424_01_00_05_0.text: Neo Tachyon will annihilate every one of your Numbers!

V0424_01_00_06_0.text: Stepping in my way is a serious mistake!

V0424_01_00_07_0.text: I believe our Galaxy-Eyes want to Duel more than us!

V0424_01_00_08_0.text: You may possess a Galaxy-Eyes, but can you control it?

V0424_01_00_09_0.text:
Kite!
You'll learn that I'm the true master of Galaxy-Eyes!

V0424_01_00_10_0.text: Time to bring our clash to an end, Kite!

V0424_01_00_11_0.text: Let's find out who's truly one with their dragons!

V0424_01_00_12_0.text:
Kite Tenjo!
I could ask for no greater rival than you!

V0424_01_00_13_0.text:
Don Thousand...
You will not go unpunished!

V0424_03_00_00_0.text: Beneath your tough exterior hides a terrified child!

V0424_03_00_01_0.text: Why continue to fight when you know you won't survive?

V0424_03_00_04_0.text: You are a fool if you think I'm actually in trouble!

V0424_03_00_05_0.text: Your silly strategies will not work forever!

V0424_05_00_00_0.text:
It's not over!
Not when Neo Tachyon rules the galaxy!

V0424_07_09_00_0.text: I flip over my Set card!

V0424_11_01_00_0.text: I Summon a monster in Defense Position!

V0424_16_00_00_0.text: With this final attack, you are reduced to nothing!

V0424_21_00_00_0.text:
Humph!
You can't hold on forever!

V0424_21_00_01_0.text:
Stand up and fight.
I need you to keep Dueling!

V0424_21_00_04_0.text:
You shouldn't underestimate me.
You haven't won yet!

V0424_21_00_05_0.text: I've had enough of your tricks!

V0424_28_00_00_0.text:
Humans are so fragile.
My dragon was only toying with you!

V0424_28_00_01_0.text:
Heh.
As if any other outcome was possible.

V0424_28_00_02_0.text: You were no match for Tachyon Dragon - nor will you ever be!

V0424_28_00_03_0.text:
Hahahaha!
Neo Tachyon is the mightiest of dragons!

V0424_28_00_04_0.text:
Neo Tachyon can control time.
What can your monsters do?

V0424_28_00_05_0.text:
Hahahaha!
I'm the true Galaxy-Eyes master - not you!

V0424_28_00_06_0.text:
Hahaha!
A fitting end to a battle between Galaxy-Eyes!

V0424_28_00_07_0.text: Never challenge me with your pathetic dragons again, Kite!

V0424_28_00_09_0.text:
Don Thousand!
The future you're creating isn't what we want!

V0424_29_00_00_0.text:
I'll withdraw for now.
But I will defeat you next time!

V0424_29_00_03_0.text:
I don't believe it...
You defeated my Tachyon Dragon?

V0424_29_00_04_0.text:
Impossible...
How can anyone overcome Tachyon's effect?

V0424_29_00_05_0.text:
Grr...
Don't you dare feel sorry for me!

V0424_29_00_06_0.text: So that's the power of your Number...

V0424_29_00_07_0.text: You were victorious this Duel, but you won't win the next!

V0424_29_00_08_0.text:
Kite!
I won't stop until I rule all forms of Galaxy-Eyes!

V0424_29_00_09_0.text: I underestimated the strength of your family...

V0424_29_00_10_0.text: It's clear that you taught Kite everything he knows.

V0424_29_00_11_0.text:
Nash... Yuma... Astral...
I'm counting on you...

V0424_33_00_01_0.text: You deserve to face my very best!

V0424_33_00_03_0.text: Watch as I unleash the power of the dragons!

V0424_43_00_00_0.text: You've proven worthy of facing my true strength!

V0424_30_00_00_0.text:
Give it your best.
Though you know it won't be enough.

V0424_30_00_01_0.text: If you can't stand up, the honorable choice is to surrender.

V0424_30_00_02_0.text: You're realizing you lost your only chance to win.

V0424_34_00_01_0.text: That's so few damage it'll take you a billion turns to win!

V0424_34_00_02_0.text: There's only one choice you can make!

V0424_34_00_04_0.text: It must be maddening trying to survive with such weaklings.

V0424_34_00_05_0.text:
What!?
You're ending your turn without doing anything?

V0424_34_00_06_0.text: Only a coward would play that card!

V0424_34_00_07_0.text: I can hear the roar of your dragon!

V0424_34_00_08_0.text: Heh. You're more trouble than you're worth.

V0424_34_00_09_0.text:
Why so impatient, Tachyon?
That eager to fight?

V0424_34_00_10_0.text: I now understand why Tachyon Dragon was so excited.

V0424_34_00_11_0.text:
I can call Neo Tachyon anytime to help me-
...Oh no!

V0424_34_00_12_0.text: The dragons will end you - even if it costs me everything!

V0424_32_00_01_0.text:
Whoa...
So this is Yu-Gi-Oh! Duel Links!

V0424_35_00_00_0.text:
I am Mizar!
The true master of Galaxy-Eyes!

V0424_35_00_01_0.text:
My name is Mizar!
No one commands dragons like I do!

V0424_36_00_00_0.text:
There's no need for mercy.
Finish them!

V0424_36_00_01_0.text: Just do the best you can.

V0424_36_00_02_0.text: I don't need your help, but I have no choice.

V0424_36_00_04_0.text: Even I'm curious to know how strong your Galaxy-Eyes is!

V0424_36_00_05_0.text: I leave the rest to you, Dumon!

V0424_27_00_02_0.text: How could this be happening to me?

V0424_08_00_00_0.text: I will show you the true power of the Barians!

V0424_08_00_01_0.text: I drew the perfect card for this moment!

V0424_08_00_02_0.text:
Here I go!
Barian's Chaos Draw!

V0424_08_00_03_0.text:
I activate my Field Spell!
Barian Untopia!

V0424_08_00_04_0.text: The Field Spell Barian Untopia's effect activates!

V0424_08_00_05_0.text: I activate my Spell Card, Seventh Ascension!

V0424_08_00_06_0.text: Seventh Ascension's effect activates from my Graveyard!

V0424_08_00_07_0.text:
I activate my Quick-Play Spell!
Seventh Force!

V0424_08_00_08_0.text: I activate the Spell Card, Galactic Charity!

V0424_08_00_09_0.text: I activate the Quick-Play Spell, Saga of the Dragon Emperor!

V0424_08_00_10_0.text: I banish Saga of the Dragon Emperor from my Graveyard!

V0424_08_00_11_0.text:
Allow me to play this!
I activate the Spell, Monster Reborn!

V0424_08_00_12_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Tachyon Spiral Galaxy!

V0424_08_00_13_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Tachyon Chaos Hole!

V0424_08_00_14_0.text: I activate Tachyon Chaos Hole's effect from my Graveyard!

V0424_08_00_15_0.text:
My Counter Trap activates!
Tachyon Transmigration!

V0424_08_00_16_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Rebirth of the Seventh Emperors!

V0424_08_00_17_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Reincarnation of the Seventh Emperors!

V0424_08_00_18_0.text:
I activate my Continuous Trap!
Seventh Eternity!

V0424_09_00_00_0.text: I activate Galaxy-Eyes Tachyon Dragon's effect!

V0424_09_00_01_0.text: I use 1 Overlay Unit to activate Tachyon Dragon's effect!

V0424_09_00_02_0.text: Neo Galaxy-Eyes Tachyon Dragon uses 1 Chaos Overlay Unit!

V0424_09_00_03_0.text: As long as I have Neo Tachyon, there's nothing you can do!

V0424_09_00_04_0.text: I activate Neo Tachyon's additional effect!

V0424_09_00_04_1.text: By Tributing 2 monsters, Neo Tachyon can attack 3 times!

V0424_09_00_05_0.text: I use 1 Overlay Unit to activate Dragluon's effect!

V0424_09_00_06_0.text: I use 1 Overlay Unit to activate Draglubion's effect!

V0424_09_00_07_0.text: I use 1 Overlay Unit to play Galaxy Stealth Dragon's effect!

V0424_09_00_08_0.text: I banish Galaxy Satellite Dragon to activate its effect!

V0424_09_00_09_0.text: Galaxy Satellite Dragon's effect activates this End Phase!

V0424_09_00_11_0.text: I banish Starliege Seyfert from my Graveyard!

V0424_09_00_12_0.text: I activate Nebula Dragon's effect from my hand!

V0424_09_00_13_0.text: I banish Nebula Dragon from my Graveyard to use its effect!

V0424_09_00_15_0.text: Galactic Spiral Dragon activates its effect!

V0424_37_00_00_0.text: A behemoth with the ability to bend time to do its will!

V0424_13_00_00_0.text:
Arise!
For we shall claim victory for Barian!

V0424_13_00_01_0.text:
Appear in all your fearsome terror!
Number 107!

V0424_37_00_01_0.text: Barian power born from chaos, surge through my Number!

V0424_37_00_01_1.text: Face the multiverse and ignite new life into my great beast!

V0424_13_00_02_0.text: Number C107: Neo Galaxy-Eyes Tachyon Dragon!

V0424_37_00_02_0.text: Face the multiverse and ignite new life into my great beast!

V0424_13_00_03_0.text:
Come forth!
Number C107: Neo Galaxy-Eyes Tachyon Dragon!

V0424_37_00_03_1.text: Face the multiverse and ignite new life into my great beast!

V0424_37_00_04_0.text:
Number 46!
Roar with the thunder!
Crash with the lightning!

V0424_37_00_05_0.text:
Number 97!
Quake the atmosphere!
Swirl the black flames!

V0424_19_00_02_0.text:
Galaxy-Eyes Tachyon Dragon!
Rewind time to manifest again!

V0424_19_00_03_0.text:
Here we go!
Neo Galaxy-Eyes Tachyon Dragon!
